INSERT INTO Paragraphs (ParagraphID, TopicID, Content) VALUES (11, 5, 'Geometric Views of Complex Operations It is important to develop an ability to visualize complex number operations. This is done by plotting the vectors that represent the numbers in the plane, where and. The key to this is to recall that, as shown in Fig.~※, the complex number is a vector whose tail is at the origin and whose head is at.');
